<HEADLINE> Indian PM Initiates Consensus on CTBT </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, December 17 (Xinhua) -- Indian Prime Minister Atal
Bihari Vajpayee Friday initiated the process of evolving a
consensus on the question of Comprehensive Test Ban Treaty (CTBT)
by holding consultations with the Congress on the issue.
</P>
