<TEXT>
<P>
MACAO, December 18 (Xinhua) -- Portuguese President Jorge
Sampaio said here Saturday night that the success of the
transition of Macao has enhanced the relations between Portugal
and China and will guide the future development of such relations.
</P>
<P>
Sampaio, who is here for the handover ceremony, attributed the
success to the joint effort of the leaders of both countries on
the basis of mutual respect.
</P>
<P>
