<HEADLINE> HKSAR, Italy Sign Pact on Transfer of Sentenced Persons </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, December 18 (Xinhua) -- The Hong Kong Special
Administrative Region (HKSAR) and Italy signed an agreement on the
transfer of sentenced persons here Saturday.
</P>
<P>
The agreement was signed by the Secretary for Security of the
HKSAR, Regina Ip, and Italian Deputy Minister of Foreign Affairs
Senator Valentino Martelli.
</P>
<P>
