another important step forward in building cooperation between
Hong Kong and Italy in the area of criminal justice and
international law enforcement," Ip said at the signing ceremony.
</P>
<P>
Since Hong Kong's return to China, the government of the HKSAR
has signed similar agreements with the United Kingdom, the United
States and Sri Lanka. 
