<TEXT>
<P>
BELGRADE, December 18 (Xinhua) -- Gro Marit Istad of Norway
claimed her first title in a Biathlon World Cup when she won the
women's 7.5 kilometer sprint Saturday in Pokljuka, Slovenia.
</P>
<P>
