<HEADLINE> Weekly Highlights of Diplomatic News (3) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
-- Chinese Premier Zhu Rongji, in talks with Czech Prime
Minister Milos Zeman Thursday, said that Sino-Czech relations will
develop even further in the 21st century in a more stable and
sound manner. Zeman arrived Thursday for a three-day official
