are missing and about 200 dead," Rangel said, adding the figures
were for the capital city of 6 million people and seven other
states including the tourist island of Margarita.
</P>
<P>
President Hugo Chavez toured disaster zones dressed in
camouflage military fatigues. He said Thursday that it was the
worst tragedy in Venezuela in 50 years. 
